      "rationale": "Three mesh levels (coarse ~180k, medium ~420k, fine ~950k elements) were analysed. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI values of 0.9%, 1.1%, and 1.4% for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm respectively. All below 2% threshold. Monotonic convergence confirmed. Discretization error adequately characterised."
