      "rationale": "The validation activity is co-extensive with the COU: same device design (non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw), same test standard (ASTM F1717), same loading mode (static compression-bending), same QoIs. No extrapolation beyond the validated domain is required for the regulatory submission. Validation relevance assessed as fully adequate at Gradation 3."
    }
